|GKB-- Renewal ---------------------------------------------------|000

While not as skilled in the healing arts as a cleric,
a druid does have a fair amount of knowledge of those
arts.  This Marken invocation, representing the renewal of all
things in the natural cycle, is their most potent
magical tool to that end.  It will rejuvenate a
target, completely healing all but the greatest
wounds.

|CKBCommand:      |000 renewal <target> (defaults to caster)
|CKBBase Cost:    |000 140 Marken nwyfre
|CKBBase Recovery:|000 short
|CKBBase Effect:  |000 heal (high)
|CKBBase Duration:|000 instant
|CKBGuild Level:  |000 23
